OL,3,CPolice 'under attack' and arrests made
OL,4,Cafter 2,000 people attend illegal rave
OL,6,FPolice made multiple arrests after
OL,7,F2,000 people showed up to an illegal
OL,8,Frave in Dorset at the weekend.
OL,10,FThe "unauthorised music event" was
OL,11,Ffirst reported to the police at around
OL,12,F11.45pm on Saturday (4 April).
OL,14,FIt is believed that around 2,000
OL,15,Fpeople had gathered in East Lulworth,
OL,16,Fwith more than 100 vehicles parked up
OL,17,Fin the area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
