OL,3,CPolice 'under attack' and arrests made
OL,4,Cafter 2,000 people attend illegal rave
OL,6,FOfficers came under attack and faced a
OL,7,F"hostile reception" according to
OL,8,FDorset Police, however they remained
OL,9,Fon-site until the event was brought to
OL,10,Fa "safe conclusion".
OL,12,FPolice seized equipment under section
OL,13,F64 of the Criminal Justice and Public
OL,14,FOrder Act 1994.
OL,16,FTen people were also arrested over
OL,17,Foffences including driving while under
OL,18,Fthe influence and assaulting an
OL,19,Femergency worker.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
