OL,3,CPolice 'under attack' and arrests made
OL,4,Cafter 2,000 people attend illegal rave
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Steve Lyne,
OL,7,Fof Dorset Police, said: "While
OL,8,Fresponding to the incident, our
OL,9,Fofficers came under attack from
OL,10,Fmissiles and faced a violent and
OL,11,Fhostile reception.
OL,13,F"Violence in our communities and
OL,14,Fagainst our officers will not be
OL,15,Ftolerated.
OL,26,@oD@YOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
