PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775589083
OL,3,CPolice 'under attack' and arrests made
OL,4,Cafter 2,000 people attend illegal rave
OL,6,F"These types of events are illegal and
OL,7,Fcause a significant disruption to
OL,8,Fcommunities ` we must respond to
OL,9,Fensure the safety of everyone and it
OL,10,Fis unacceptable that we are faced with
OL,11,Fviolence while doing so.
OL,13,F"We will continue now to review
OL,14,Fevidence from the scene to identify
OL,15,Fany further offences committed and
OL,16,Fdetailed enquiries will be carried
OL,17,Fout."
OL,26,@yD@EO]
