OL,3,CPolice 'under attack' and arrests made
OL,4,Cafter 2,000 people attend illegal rave
OL,6,FMeanwhile the county's Police and
OL,7,FCrime Commissioner says the incident
OL,8,Fhas had a significant impact on
OL,9,Fresidents.
OL,11,FPolice and Crime Commissioner David
OL,12,FSidwick said: "We would like to thank
OL,13,Fthe local community for their
OL,14,Funderstanding while the police and
OL,15,Flocal agencies put in action plans to
OL,16,Fdisperse the event.
OL,26,@tD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
