OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775589083
OL,3,CPolice 'under attack' and arrests made
OL,4,Cafter 2,000 people attend illegal rave
OL,6,F"This has had a significant impact on
OL,7,Fresidents and visitors and the
OL,8,Fauthorities took swift, proportionate
OL,9,Faction, using powers available to
OL,10,Fthem, as soon as it was possible.
OL,12,F"I would like to thank everyone who
OL,13,Fwas involved in this policing
OL,14,Foperation, including officers from
OL,15,FDorset Police and elsewhere across the
OL,16,Fcountry, who worked together to bring
OL,17,Fthe incident to a safe conclusion.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
