OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1775589083
OL,3,CPolice 'under attack' and arrests made
OL,4,Cafter 2,000 people attend illegal rave
OL,6,F"We will not tolerate unlicensed music
OL,7,Fevents because of the increased risks
OL,8,Fthey present and the impact they have
OL,9,Fon our communities and those visiting
OL,10,Fthe area."
